Description: The rest on the flight into Egypt, with the Holy Family succoured by angels, in a landscape. Etching
Producer name: Print made by: Pier Francesco Mola
Curator's comments: According to Bartsch, finished by an anonymous engraver who added the angel leading the donkey to left and part of the wings of the angel kneeling before Christ.
Acquisition name: Bequeathed by: Clayton Mordaunt Cracherode (with Philipe's blindstamp and initials CMC)
